<note id="fs-idm221035232" class="os-teacher">
<title>Standards</title>
<para id="fs-idm215957712"><emphasis effect="bold">Topic:</emphasis> 1.7 Causation in Period 1</para>
<para id="fs-idm222931424"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objective:</emphasis> Unit 1G Explain the effects of the development of transatlantic voyages from 1491 to 1607</para>
<para id="fs-idm238867808"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Developments:</emphasis> 1.1.I, 1.2.I, 1.2.II, 1.2.III</para>
<para id="fs-idm225719296"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Thinking Skill:</emphasis> HTS-6 Argumentation</para>
